name: Sining
description:
A few years from now,
you'll be brought into the world by your mother
And the first thing that I'll do is to give thanks unto the Father
I'll learn every bit of you at first sight by heart 
On how you were formed and molded


You have a beautiful name, Sining
Just by your name, I know you're worth loving
If you grow up and ask me why we chose that name
I'll always tell you that you are a galaxy

You'll be confused.
It's complicated.
You won't understand.
And this is not about your gender
You'll get different opinions in every place that you'll go
But you'll not accept it right away
You're a human that won't be controlled by the world, Sining.
You'll always be the color that won't fade even in the darkest place

And if you won't be good in any field that is anchored in your name
Remember that excellence is not all this world needs
But a person who knows how to listen and learn
when he doesn't know a thing


Sining is a Filipino word for Art.
